<blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex"><div id=":6v1" style="overflow:hidden">For example, if you build and run the test like this:<br>
<br>
make check<br>
./opal_path_nfs . Makefile ~<br>
<br>
It&#39;ll report if ., Makefile, and ~ are on network filesystems (i.e., the result of sending each of &quot;.&quot;, &quot;Makefile&quot;, and &quot;your_home_dir&quot; to opal_path_nfs()).</div></blockquote></div><br><br>
